        <tr id="comment-body-359023"><td bgcolor="#ffffff">
            <p>In the ideal scenario, Advent ingestion is turned back on in time to include. If not, then clone this ticket, update the clone to be for Advent only, and update this ticket to be for MLH and BH only. Furthermore, the cloned ticket will likely need it’s own normalization tickets.</p>
        </td></tr>
