        <tr id="comment-body-364707"><td bgcolor="#ffffff">
            <p>From Sammed today:</p>

<p>Hi Connor, here is the test output of the medication tables with flat structure and one with doses separated out in a table. I'm continuing working on getting it standardized to IN/ MIN level. These tables are in process to be pushed to production. Let me know if you have any questions. </p>

<p>Here is the PR that has the output tables: <a href="https://github.com/N-Power-Medicine/databricks_etl/pull/662" title="smart-link" class="external-link" rel="nofollow noreferrer">https://github.com/N-Power-Medicine/databricks_etl/pull/662</a> </p>

<p>Jira ticket is here: <a href="https://n-power.atlassian.net/browse/DE-276" title="smart-link" class="external-link" rel="nofollow noreferrer">https://n-power.atlassian.net/browse/DE-276</a> </p>
        </td></tr>
