                    Connor Sweetnam
                </a>

                                        <font size="-2">
            [
                <font color="#336699">24/Mar/26</font>

                            ]
            </font>

        </td></tr>
        <tr id="comment-body-365708"><td bgcolor="#ffffff">
            <p>Questions for Sammed:</p>

<ul>
	<li>How flat is medications_flat?
	<ul>
		<li>dosage, ingredient, etc.</li>
		<li>Drug and doses exploded</li>
	</ul>
	</li>
	<li>What was used to map to rxcui?
	<ul>
		<li>Used development.test_ai_ms.rxnorm_kbtherapy_441_2506_unnested</li>
		<li>Which column should I filter on?
		<ul>
			<li>ingredient code and ingredient code display</li>
			<li>generic name and code seem to have multiple ingredients or precise ingredients (salt isomers)</li>
		</ul>
		</li>
	</ul>
	</li>
	<li>Brad says to use spmd_sqa.maps.rxnorm_kbtherapy for now</li>
</ul>

